description:
In this beautiful and heartfelt holiday karaoke rendition of "Angels We Have Heard On High," we pay tribute to all the wonderful angels who have helped us along our journey. From special people in our lives to loved ones lost, this song speaks to everyone who has ever been touched by angels.
Merry Christmas everyone! This special rendition of "Angels We Have Heard On High" will bring some happiness into your life this holiday season. Listen and let the angels sing praise to God!

Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters  youtube production!
Motion Graphics Used : NOYA STUDIO - THE KING OF MOTION GRAPHICS https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCKJh...
